    "data_size": 182,
    "nom_orig": "Head[SP]monk",
    "texte_orig": "Is[SP]that[SP]the[SP]rumored[SP]Leonids...?[1205][001E][SP]Indeed,[SP]it\nlooks[SP]as[SP]if[SP]a[SP]lion[SP]is[SP]roaring.",
