    "data_size": 278,
    "nom_orig": "Young[SP]monk",
    "texte_orig": "Your[SP]hairstyle[SP]is[SP]so[SP]cool![SP]What[SP]is[SP]that,\na[SP]pageboy?[SP]I[SP]wish[SP]I[SP]could[SP]give[SP]it[SP]a[SP]try,\nbut[SP]there's[SP]the[SP]whole[SP]shaved-head[SP]thing.",
